token_info.description: An interactive catalogue NFT for Pippa Darbyshire's debut exhibition with @FineNFT. Browse all 12 expressive abstract paintings of ships in the series and read more about the artist. All paintings will be available as hi-res authenticated 1/1 editions via hic.link/fine. Menu icon top left = options for slideshow, dark/light mode etc. It is responsive design but best viewed on desktop, esp. full screen). Navigation with cursor keys also works. Gallery built by @1x1_NFT.
